description:
Have you seen the video of Dr. Stella Immanuel?? I think it’s worth the watch for sure. With a group of doctors she went to DC and gave a speech that you need to hear. According to the doctor and I quote :”Patients that have diabetes, patients that have high blood pressure, patients that have asthma, old people … I think my oldest patient is 92 … 87 year olds. And the result has been the same. I put them on hydroxychloroquine, I put them on zinc, I put them on Zithromax, and they’re all well.” She basically yelled that people don’t need to die!! What do you think about that?? Why do you think the media isn’t picking up this story more? Why isn’t this front news 24/7? Because it doesn’t fit the narrative? Because it would mean the government is wrong? The lockdown should have never happened? Nobody should have ever died? We shouldn’t be waiting for the vaccine? They shouldn’t have spend billions of dollars into the development of the vaccines? That money could have been used in a million other ways that would have impacted the lives of so many people? Why? Why? Why? ✌️
